t%3D%5C%22Murad%20Retinol%20Youth%20Renewal%20Serum%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6841dc819b2a601d01b26676%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221043%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20few%20times%20a%20week%2C%20Paul%20swaps%20her%20prescription%20tretinoin%20for%20a%20gentler%20retinol%3A%20Murad%20Retinol%20Youth%20Renewal%20Serum.%3Cp%3EMurad%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3EPaul%20starts%20by%20double-cleansing%2C%20first%20with%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-tried-using-olive-oil-cleanser-just-like-celebrities-do-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoil-based%20cleanser%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Clinique%20Take%20The%20Day%20Off%20Cleansing%20Balm)%20to%20remove%20sunscreen%20and%20eye%20makeup.%20She%20then%20finishes%20with%20her%20morning%20cleanser%20(La%20Roche-Posay%20Toleriane%20Purifying%20Foaming%20Cleanser).%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20uses%20either%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fretinol-vs-retin-a-vs-retinoid%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprescription-strength%20retinoid%3C%2Fa%3E%20(tretinoin)%2C%20which%20increases%20cell%20turnover%20and%20boosts%20collagen%20production%20for%20more%20youthful-looking%20skin.%20When%20her%20skin%20is%20feeling%20sensitive%2C%20she%20instead%20uses%20a%20gentler%2C%20over-the-counter%20retinol%20(Murad%20Retinol%20Youth%20Renewal%20Firming%20%26amp%3B%20Smoothing%20Serum%20with%20Hyaluronic%20Acid).%20%26quot%3BI've%20been%20using%20tretinoin%20for%2010%20years%20%E2%80%94%20even%20then%2C%20I%20cannot%20do%20it%20every%20single%20night%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20applies%20the%20same%20moisturizer%20she%20used%20in%20the%20morning%20(CeraVe%20Daily%20Moisturizing%20Lotion%20or%20Neutrogena%20Hydro%20Boost%20Water%20Gel).%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20last%20step%20is%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-eye-creams-fine-lines-dark-circles-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeye%20cream%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Dr.%20Dennis%20Gross%20Skincare%20DermInfusions%20Fill%20%2B%20Repair%20Eye%20Cream)%20to%20hydrate%20her%20under-eye%20area%20more.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b5a764ed-0213-4be6-89f7-be6fb443f9f0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EShe%20also%20exfoliates%20and%20practices%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-skin-cycling-how-tiktok-trend-heals-routine-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3Eskin-cycling%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221006%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ZO%20Skin%20Health%20Exfoliating%20Polish%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6841dd769b2a601d01b2669f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22755%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPaul%20likes%20the%20texture%20of%20ZO%20Skin%20Health's%20Exfoliating%20Polish.%3Cp%3EZO%20Skin%20Health%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPaul%20exfoliates%20her%20skin%20a%20few%20times%20a%20week%20to%20unclog%20her%20pores%20and%20soften%20her%20skin.%20After%20cleansing%20her%20skin%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20she%20applies%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fskincare-trends-we-loved-2000s-new-improved-techniques-2023-2%23weve-swapped-hard-scrubs-for-gentler-exfoliants-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echemical%20exfoliant%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Paula's%20Choice%202%25%20BHA%20Liquid%20Exfoliant)%20or%20a%20scrub%20(ZO%20Skin%20Health%20Exfoliating%20Polish).%20She%20said%20which%20one%20you%20use%20should%20be%20%26quot%3Bbased%20on%20how%20sensitive%20or%20dry%20your%20skin%20feels.%26quot%3B%20After%20that%20step%2C%20she%20adds%20moisturizer%20and%20sunscreen%2C%20omitting%20any%20serums%20that%20could%20irritate%20her%20skin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20changes%20her%20skincare%20routine%20depending%20on%20the%20season.%20In%20the%20winter%2C%20when