12a13c8c2c%5C%22%3E3.%20Stock-based%20compensation%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20have%20any%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foptions-opportunism-executive-stock-grant-timing-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estock-based%20compensation%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20your%20employer%2C%20like%20me%2C%20those%20stocks%20typically%20vest%20in%20a%20holding%20account%20at%20a%20bank.%20In%20that%20holding%20account%2C%20the%20stock%20is%20technically%20yours%20once%20it%20vests%2C%20but%20you%20can't%20diversify%2C%20sell%20it%2C%20or%20invest%20it%20in%20anything%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20manage%20the%20stock%2C%20you'll%20need%20to%20move%20it%20into%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fbest-online-brokerage%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebrokerage%20account%3C%2Fa%3E.%20You%20can%20transfer%20it%20within%20the%20same%20financial%20institution%20that%20holds%20your%20holding%20account%2C%20or%20use%20your%20own%20personal%20banking%20institution%20to%20move%20it%20into%20a%20brokerage%20account.%20Once%20it's%20in%20the%20brokerage%20account%2C%20you%20can%20manage%20it%20based%20on%20your%20financial%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20don't%20oppose%20moving%20it%20to%20a%20brokerage%20account%2C%20but%20you%20have%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20to%20do%20with%20it%20yourself.%20They%20don't%20always%20tell%20you%20that%20when%20you%20quit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20some%20financial%20benefits%20to%20moving%20it%20out%20of%20the%20holding%20account.%20I%20got%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fhow-to-get-a-lower-mortgage-interest-rate%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elower%20interest%20rate%20on%20my%20home%20mortgage%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20moving%20my%20stock%20to%20a%20brokerage%20account%20at%20a%20specific%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22345da077-c2f5-489c-a8e7-bd980aaa35dd%5C%22%3E4.%20Medical%20benefits%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20important%20to%20use%20your%20medical%20benefits%20before%20you%20leave.%20You%20likely%20already%20contributed%20to%20your%20plan%20via%20your%20paycheck%20for%20the%20portion%20of%20the%20year%20you%20were%20employed.%20Before%20quitting%2C%20I%20made%20a%20plan%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwant-whole-life-insurance-husband-term-life-insurance-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eget%20on%20my%20husband's%20insurance%20plan%20through%20his%20employer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20I%20still%20wish%20I%20had%20maxed%20out%20my%20own%20medical%20benefits%20before%20quitting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20my%20vision%20insurance%2C%20I%20could've%20received%20a%20free%20pair%20of%20glasses%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20get%20them.%20After%20I%20quit%2C%20I%20thought%20to%20myself%2C%20%3Cem%3EI%20should've%20bought%20my%20glasses%20before%20I%20left.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20others%2C%20this%20might%20also%20include%20attending%20all%20of%20your%20doctor%20and%20dentist%20appointments%20or%20really%20anything%20covered%20by%20your%20existing%20insurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20I%20knew%20about%20these%20things%2C%20I%20didn't%20prioritize%20them%2C%20so%20I%20definitely%20left%20some%20money%20on%20the%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ae06021c-f24e-4bcc-a384-b982aae29c53%5C%22%3E5.%20Transit%20benefits%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20my%20old%20job%2C%20we%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupercommuter-travels-4-states-get-work-earns-6-figures-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etransit%20benefits%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20pre-tax%20dollars%20could%20be%20used%20for%20commuting.%20I%20took%20the%20bus%20or%20train%20daily%20and%20paid%20for%20those%20with%20my%20commuter%20benefits.%20If%20I%20ever%20had%20to%20pay%20to%20park%2C%20I%20could%20use%20them%20for%20that%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wish%20I%20had%20maxed%20those%20out%20and%20paid%20for%20a%20large%20Met