rket-outlook-recession-risk-cyclical-defensive-stocks-ratio-valuations-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edoesn't%20spell%20recession%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20and%20of%20itself.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20an%20economist%2C%20and%20I%20read%20all%20of%20this%20stuff%2C%20just%20like%20you%20do.%20And%20if%20you%20do%20read%20that%20stuff%2C%20you%20know%2C%20we%20should%20have%20had%20a%20recession%20last%20year%2C%20and%20one%20the%20year%20before%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20those%20predictions%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20wrong.%20And%20so%20I%20think%20the%20word%20is%20uncertainty.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20so%20many%20factors%20up%20in%20the%20air%2C%20Smith%20says%20the%20only%20thing%20you%20can%20be%20sure%20of%20in%20today's%20economy%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvestors-economic-optimism-no-recession-jobs-report-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunpredictability%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20hard%20to%20predict%20what's%20gonna%20happen%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-us-economy-growth-oecd-forecasts-inflation-jobs-incomes-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etariffs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20what's%20gonna%20happen%20with%20bond%20yields%2C%20what's%20gonna%20happen%20with%20interest%20rates%2C%20what's%20gonna%20happen%20with%20the%20housing%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20so%2C%20all%20I%20can%20say%20is%20we%20see%20an%20increase%20in%20tasker%20applications.%20I'm%20not%20sure%20that%20that's%20an%20indication%20that%20a%20recession%20is%20coming.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20platform%2C%20the%20best%20way%20we%20can%20help%20our%20Tasker%20community%20is%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20our%20platform%20is%20delivering%20the%20opportunities%20that%20they%20are%20looking%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C