er%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Form%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStruggling%20to%20find%20work%3F%20Please%20fill%20out%20this%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2F1GdlkA_t8KsPl9wjqoOqpV1M-DQkv9TmgfN6K8CsPhtM%2Fedit%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Form%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2244aff9be-7480-49fa-a717-7fd6ef436aa2%5C%22%3ECoaching%20your%20references%20could%20help%20you%20stand%20out%20from%20the%20crowd%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20Cohan%20said%20he's%20overseen%2015%20full-time%20hires%20across%20Halmos%20Capital%20and%20its%20six%20portfolio%20companies%2C%20which%20together%20employ%20hundreds%20of%20people.%20He's%20also%20played%20a%20direct%20role%20in%20selecting%20nine%20C-suite%20executives%20or%20board%20members.%20At%20the%20firm%20itself%2C%20which%20employs%20eight%20professionals%2C%20Cohan%20is%20involved%20in%20everything%20from%20summer%20intern%20interviews%20to%20executive%20placements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20nearly%20every%20full-time%20role%2C%20the%20firm%20aims%20to%20speak%20with%20five%20to%20eight%20references.%20Cohan%20said%20he%20conducts%20many%20of%20the%20reference%20calls%2C%20asking%20for%20detailed%20feedback%2C%20both%20positive%20and%20negative.%20He%20looks%20for%20specifics%20%E2%80%94%20not%20vague%20endorsements%20%E2%80%94%20and%20consistency%20across%20what%20the%20candidate%2C%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%2C%20and%20references%20are%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20get%20references%20who%20just%20say%2C%20'Hey%2C%20he's%20a%20good%20person%2C%20she's%20a%20good%20worker%2C%20I%20like%20them%2C'%20that's%20just%20filler%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20what%20they're%20not%20saying%20that%20we%20listen%20to.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECohan%20said%20the%20firm%20spent%20nearly%20a%20year%20filling%20a%20senior%20associate%20role%20and%20evaluated%20over%20a%20dozen%20candidates%20before%20making%20an%20offer.%20The%20candidate%20who%20was%20ultimately%20hired%20had%20strong%20and%20detailed%20references.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20thinks%20candidates%20should%20consider%20%26quot%3Bcoaching%26quot%3B%20their%20references%20%E2%80%94%20reaching%20out%20before%20the%20company%20calls%20%E2%80%94%20to%20help%20them%20provide%20detailed%2C%20authentic%20feedback%20about%20their%20skills%20and%20accomplishments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCoaching%20references%20to%20give%20a%20great%20in-depth%20description%20of%20who%20they%20are%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20not%20going%20to%20backfire%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20they're%20positive%2C%20get%20into%20the%20details%2C%20and%20give%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20negative%20so%20that%20it%20sounds%20authentic%2C%20it's%20only%20going%20to%20set%20you%20apart.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECohan%20acknowledged%20that%20his%20firm%20might%20value%20references%20more%20than%20some%20employers%2C%20but%20said%20he%20thinks%20thoughtful%2C%20detailed%20endorsements%20can%20help%20candidates%20stand%20out%20in%20any%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222f7ab1f5-0adc-4f2b-83bd-aea0cd3aa4e4%5C%22%3EHonesty%20could%20be%20the%20best%20policy%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20interviews%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETrying%20to%20hide%20certain%20details%20about%20one's%20background%20or%20work%20experience%20could%20backfire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECohan%20recalled%20a%20candidate%20for%20a%20CEO%20role%20who%20had%20the%20right%20credentials%20but%20raised%20questions%20his%20team%20couldn't%20fully%20answer%20%E2%80%94%20including%20why%20he'd%20left%20previous%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20nothing%20bad%20per%20se%2C%26quot%3B%20Cohan%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20there%20were%20just%20too%20many%20unknowns.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20instance%2C%20Cohan%20said%20a%20candidate%20had%20a%20sensitive%20issue%20in%20their%20background.%20Rather%20than%20trying%20to%20hide%20it%2C%20he%20said%20the%20candidate%20was%20direct%2C%20explained%20what%20happened%2C%20and%20offered%20references%20who%20could%20back%20up%20their%20story.%20After%20several%20calls%20revealed%20a%20consistent%20narrative%2C%20Cohan%20said%20he%20made%20the%20hire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20all%20know%20what%20our%20negatives%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BFeel%20free%20to%20tell%20the%20potential%20employer%20the%20negatives.%20It's%20going%20to%20set%20you%20apart.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecruiters%20and%20career%20coaches%20previously%20told%20BI%20that%20candidates%20should%20generally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-to-say-in-interview-after-you-have-been-fired-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edisclose%20if%20they%20were%20laid%20off%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20if%20addressed%20properly%2C%20it%20won't%20necessarily%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flaid-off-how-to-discuss-in-job-interview-script-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehurt%20their%20chances%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e2b61112-d052-4835-a9c6-16ee05fe7941%5C%22%3EConnecting%20with%20recruiters%20could%20help%20you%20find%20positions%20that%20are%20the%20best%20fit%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECohan%20said%20his%20firm%20relies%20on%20specialized%20executive%20recruiters%20to%20source%20candidates%20for%20positions%20like%20associates%20and%20VPs.%20These%20recruiters%20might%20sift%20through%20hundreds%20of%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20before%20presenting%20Cohan%20with%20a%20shortlist%20of%20around%20a%20dozen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20in%20investment%20funds%20are%20very%20busy%2C%26quot%3B%20Cohan%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20get%20hit%20with%20a%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20randomly%2C%20we%20may%20not%20have%20time%20to%20look%20at%20it.%20We%20certainly%20don't%20have%20time%20to%20read%20a%20cover%20letter.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECohan%20recommended%20that%20job%20seekers%20connect%20with%20recrui