lf-driving%20cars%2C%20Uber%20has%20shifted%20strategy%20and%20struck%20a%20spree%20of%20deals%20to%20add%20robotaxis%20operated%20by%20self-driving%20companies%20to%20its%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20a%20partnership%20with%20Google-backed%20Waymo%20to%20operate%20its%20autonomous%20taxis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-ceo-robotaxis-austin-are-busier-than-most-human-drivers-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eon%20the%20Uber%20platform%20in%20Austin%20and%20Phoenix%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20has%20signed%20similar%20deals%20with%20Chinese%20robotaxi%20startups%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweride-ceo-explains-how-uber-deal-help-make-robotaxis-safer-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWeRide%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Pony.AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUber%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finvestor.uber.com%2Fnews-events%2Fnews%2Fpress-release-details%2F2024%2FWayve-and-Uber-Partner-to-Accelerate-the-Future-of-Automated-Driving%2Fdefault.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einked%20its%20deal%20with%20Wayve%20last%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20agreeing%20to%20deploy%20self-driving%20vehicles%20powered%20by%20the%20British%20startup's%20technology%20on%20its%20platform%20in%20multiple%20markets%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUber%20also%20invested%20in%20Wayve%20through%20an%20extension%20of%20the%20company's%20Series%20C%20fundraising%20round%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwayve.ai%2Fpress%2Fseries-c%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraised%20%241.05%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20investors%20including%20Softbank%2C%20Nvidia%2C%20and%20Microsoft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20London-based%20startup%2C%20which%20has%20been%20testing%20its%20fleet%20of%20autonomous%20Ford%20Mach-Es%20with%20a%20safety%20driver%20in%20London%20for%20several%20years%2C%20has%20quickly%20become%20one%20of%20the%20buzziest%20names%20in%20the%20robotaxi%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWayve%20says%20its%20%26quot%3BAI%20driver%26quot%3B%20runs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwayve-ceo-testing-driverless-cars-us-expansion-ai-robotics-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eon%20an%20end-to-end%20AI%20model%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20an%20approach%20also%20adopted%20by%20Tesla%20%E2%80%94%20allowing%20it%20to%20react%20to%20the%20physical%20world%20in%20the%20same%20way%20a%20human%20would%20and%20drive%20anywhere%2C%20unlike%20rivals%20like%20Waymo%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-early-talks-toyota-partnership-autonomous-driving-personally-owned-cars-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erely%20on%20high-definition%20maps%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20operate%20their%20robotaxis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20Business%20Insider%20from%20the%20back%20of%20a%20Wayve%20self-driving%20car%20in%20central%20London%2C%20Wayve%20CEO%20Kendall%20said%20the%20company%20had%20tested%20its%20autonomous%20vehicles%20in%2090%20cities%20over%20the%20past%2090%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20real%20demonstration%20of%20how%20well%20this%20technology%20generalizes.%20The%20diversity%20we%20saw%20on%20these%20roads%20is%20immense%2C%20from%20winding%20roads%20in%20the%20Swiss%20Alps%20and%20dirt%20tracks%20in%20Italy%20to%20diverse%20cities%20like%20Vancouver%20and%20Tokyo%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kendall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20vehicles%20in%20the%20robotaxi%20service%20in%20London%20will%20initially%20use%20a%20mixed%20suite%20of%20sensors%2C%20including%20cameras%2C%20radar%2C%20and%20lidar%20(laser-based%20sensors)%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20chaotic%20nature%20of%20London's%20roads%20made%20it%20the%20perfect%20place%20to%20trial%20Wayve's%20technology%20without%20a%20safety%20driver.%20During%20BI's%20test%20ride%2C%20Wayve's%20AI%20driver%20navigated%20a%20number%20of%20obstacles%2C%20such%20as%20roadworks%20in%20London's%20busy%20Kings%20Cross%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ambition%2