0crave%20the%20superior%20distinction%20of%20being%20the%20number%20one%20boss%20%E2%80%94%20with%20surging%20parallel%20drives%20for%20grandiosity%2C%26quot%3B%20Sonnenfeld%20says.%20%26quot%3BMusk's%20tragic%20mistake%20was%20that%20he%20forgot%20his%20role%20%E2%80%94%20as%20a%20staffer%20and%20advisor%20to%20Trump%2C%20not%20the%20primary%20character%20he%20foolishly%20believed%20himself%20to%20be%2C%20and%20even%20now%2C%20continues%20to%20overestimate%20his%20own%20importance%20and%20indispensability.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Famanda-hoover%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EAmanda%20Hoover%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider%20covering%20the%20tech%20industry.%20She%20writes%20about%20the%20biggest%20tech%20companies%20and%20trends.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmanagement-experts-grade-musk-explosive-breakup-trump-doge-tesla-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1749543061000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68472c6e85e81483682bb9a6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmanagement-experts-grade-musk-explosive-breakup-trump-doge-tesla-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20talked%20to%20management%20gurus%20about%20Musk's%20DOGE%20crashout.%20They%20told%20me%20there's%20one%20clear%20path%20for%20redemption.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ahoover%40insider.com%20(Amanda%20Hoover)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A68%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmanagement-experts-grade-musk-explosive-breakup-trump-doge-tesla-2025-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Zoom's%20CEO%20explains%20how%20he%20balances%20work%20and%20family%3A%20'I%20do%2