nflict%2C%20guess%20what%3F%20Family%20first.%20That's%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYuan%20founded%20Zoom%20in%202011%20as%20a%2041-year-old%2C%20after%20serving%20as%20the%20vice%20president%20of%20engineering%20at%20WebEx%2C%20which%20was%20later%20bought%20by%20Cisco.%20Zoom%20went%20public%20in%202019%2C%20and%20usage%20of%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzoom-neat-video-meetings-remote-work-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Evideoconferencing%20software%20%3C%2Fa%3Eexploded%20during%20pandemic-era%20remote%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZoom%20is%20valued%20at%20%2424.31%20billion%2C%20with%20Yuan%20holding%20about%2020%25%20of%20its%20shares.%20Its%20stock%20is%20up%2027.5%25%20in%20the%20past%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20podcast%2C%20Yuan%20shared%20an%20example%20where%20his%20duties%20as%20a%20CEO%20and%20father%20clashed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20hosted%20a%20Christmas%20party%20in%20San%20Jose%20on%20the%20same%20night%20as%20his%20son's%20San%20Francisco%20basketball%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20told%20our%20team%20I%20cannot%20make%20it%20on%20time%2C%20I%20need%20to%20finish%20watching%20my%20son's%20basketball%20game%20first%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20he%20watched%20all%20his%20kids'%20sports%20and%20dance%20practices%20and%20brings%20his%20laptop%2C%20but%20only%20worked%20when%20they%20were%20on%20the%20bench.%20He%20would%20return%20to%20watching%20when%20they%20got%20back%20in%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20the%20reason%20why%20I%20have%20back%20problems%20today%20%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%94%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20because%20I%20was%20sitting%20there%20for%20way%20too%20long%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYuan%20added%20that%20he%20wasn't%20happy%20for%20a%20year%20during%20his%20time%20at%20Cisco%20and%20wanted%20to%20build%20his%20own%20product.%20But%20he%20delayed%20founding%20Zoom%20because%20he%20wanted%20his%20kids%20to%20grow%20up%20