0Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20has%20joined%20hands%20with%3Cem%3E%20The%20Humsafar%20Trust%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Eone%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20oldest%20LGBTQ%2B%20organisations%2C%20to%20create%20a%20glossary%20that%20explains%20these%20common%20but%20important%20terms%20%E2%80%94%20simply%2C%20clearly%2C%20and%20with%20heart.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhether%20you%E2%80%99re%20an%20ally%20wanting%20to%20learn%20more%20or%20just%20curious%20about%20what%20words%20like%20%3Cem%3Eintersex%20or%20biphobia%3C%2Fem%3E%20truly%20mean%2C%20this%20guide%20is%20for%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20a%20small%20note%20before%20you%20dive%20in%3A%20This%20glossary%20%3Cem%3Edoes%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Enot%3C%2Fem%3E%20cover%20every%20term%20or%20represent%20everyone%20in%20the%20LGBTQ%2B%20community.%20After%20all%2C%20there%20is%20no%20single%20way%20to%20be%20LGBTQ%2B%20and%20definitely%20no%20one-size-fits-all%20way%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20identities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%20can%20be%20done%20while%20being%20respectful%3F%20Simply%20ask.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsk%20people%20how%20they%20describe%20themselves%2C%20ask%20for%20their%20pronouns%2C%20and%20reflect%20that%20in%20how%20you%20speak%20about%20them%20or%20write%20about%20them.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20language%20is%20about%20listening%2C%20and%20this%20guide%20is%20just%20a%20starting%20point%20to%20help%20us%20all%20do%20that%20a%20little%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELGBTQ%2B%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20start%20with%20the%20foundation.%20You%E2%80%99ve%20probably%20seen%20the%20acronym%20LGBTQ%20used%20often%2C%20whether%20in%20conversations%2C%20news%2C%20or%20on%20social%20me