beliefs%2C%20like%20trying%20to%20%E2%80%9Cfix%E2%80%9D%20or%20change%20someone%E2%80%99s%20sexuality%2C%20which%20is%20not%20only%20untrue%20but%20also%20very%20hurtful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20the%20right%20term%20to%20use%20is%20%E2%80%9Csexual%20orientation%E2%80%9D%20or%20just%20%E2%80%9Corientation.%E2%80%9D%20This%20refers%20to%20a%20person%E2%80%99s%20natural%20and%20lasting%20attraction%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20to%20people%20of%20the%20same%20gender%2C%20a%20different%20gender%2C%20multiple%20genders%2C%20or%20none%20at%20all.%20It%20includes%20people%20who%20are%20lesbian%2C%20gay%2C%20bisexual%2C%20queer%2C%20pansexual%2C%20and%20also%20straight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EDon%E2%80%99t%20say%20%E2%80%9Clifestyle%2C%E2%80%9D%20say%20%E2%80%9CLGBTQI%2B%20people%20and%20their%20lives%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20word%20%E2%80%9Clifestyle%E2%80%9D%20usually%20describes%20the%20way%20people%20choose%20to%20live%2C%20like%20being%20busy%2C%20relaxed%2C%20eco-friendly%2C%20or%20sporty.%20It%20is%20about%20personal%20choices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20people%20say%20%E2%80%9CLGBT%20lifestyle%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20wrongly%20suggests%20that%20being%20gay%2C%20lesbian%2C%20bi%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F436107%2Fbabli-by-night-bafta-neel-soni%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrans%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20choice%2C%20like%20picking%20a%20hobby%20or%20a%20trend.%20Being%20LGBTQI%2B%20is%20not%20a%20lifestyle%3B%20rather%2C%20it%20is%20who%20someone%20is.%20LGBTQI%2B%20people%20can%20have%20all%20kinds%20of%20lives%3A%20some%20are%20married%2C%20some%20have%20kids%2C%20some%20are%20single%2C%20and%20they%20live%20in%20all%20kinds%20of%20ways%2C%20just%20like%20anyone%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EDon%E2%80%99t%20say%20%E2%80%9Csex%20reassignment%20surgery%2C%E2%80%9D%20say%20%E2%80%9Ctransitioning%E2%80%9D%3C%2