20pocket%20is%20often%20heavier%20and%20gentler%2C%20absorbed%20by%20the%20thirsty%20roots%20of%20the%20mangroves.%20The%20Creekside%20Colony%2C%20one%20of%20three%20residential%20clusters%20near%20the%20forest%2C%20enjoys%20what%20residents%20call%20a%20%E2%80%98good%E2%80%99%20climate%E2%80%99%E2%80%94cleaner%20air%2C%20less%20heat%2C%20and%20an%20occasional%20chorus%20of%20birdsong.%20All%20of%20this%20is%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20city%20constantly%20battling%20rising%20temperatures%2C%20waterlogging%2C%20and%20air%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20is%20just%20one%20visible%20outcome%20of%20a%20much%20deeper%2C%20long-term%20commitment.%20Since%20they%20acquired%20the%20land%20in%20the%201940s%2C%20Godrej%20Enterprises%20Group%20has%20chosen%20to%20preserve%20and%20protect%20this%20mangrove%20ecosystem%2C%20not%20as%20a%20CSR%20project%2C%20not%20for%20branding%2C%20and%20not%20as%20a%20compliance%20tick%20box%E2%80%94but%20as%20an%20act%20of%20belief%E2%80%94a%20belief%20that%20business%20and%20biodiversity%20can%20exist%20harmoniously.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20even%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20a%20concrete%20jungle%2C%20a%20forest%20can%20be%20nurtured%20%E2%80%94%20if%20you%20care%20enough%20to%20protect%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20%E2%80%98wasteland%E2%80%99%20to%20ecological%20treasure%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERewind%20to%20the%201940s%20%E2%80%94%20a%20time%20when%20mangroves%20were%20largely%20misunderstood.%20Often%20dismissed%20as%20marshy%20wastelands%20or%20potential%20real%20estate%2C%20they%20were%20left%20unprotected%2C%20encroached%20upon%2C%20and%20plundered%20for%20firewood%20by%20locals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20when%20the%20late%20Sohrabji%20Godrej%2C%20a%20nature%20lover%20and%20industrialist%2C%20saw%20something%20others%20didn%E2%80%99t%20%E2%80%94%20an%20ecosystem%20worth%20preserving.%20Under%20his%20guidance%2C%20Godrej%20initiated%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20%3